cdata.name: GameX
cdata.desc: GameX is a Waves-based token that will be used on GameX'sthree major projects GameX Marketplace, GameX In-die Club and GameX GPU Mining Hub. Users can use the tokens to buy, sell and trade in-game items, key codes, game cards or even gaming hardware, they can earn GameX with each trade as well. The token also allows users to present their gaming project to the GameXcommunityin order to get it funded. Lastly, the token can be used in the GameX GPU Mining Hub.
